    "Automation of internal audits is another area seeing development.",
    "Auditors may order LLMs with instructions such, \"Verify compliance of employee onboarding processes with KYC policies,\" therefore allowing the model to examine their records, spot flaws, and suggest changes.",
    "These solutions help companies to stay compliant on their own, thus less depending on legal personnel.",
